Even with financial incentives, solar power won’t be viable for 30 years&#xD;
Volcovici 12 (Valerie, 5/1, US solar subsidies consistent with coal, oil: report http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/01/usa-solar-subsidies-idUSL1E8G15RD20120501) &#xD;
